GROUP 7 - ENERGY SAVING APPLIANCES,
MACHINERY AND EQUIPMENT
(a) fluorescent, hot cathode;
(b) light emitting diode lamps;
(c) light emitting diode modules;
(d) solar water heaters;
(e) solar panels;
(f) solar streetlights;
